  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. ",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes. ",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute. ",
    "Add the chicken liver and cook until browned, about 5 minutes. ",
    "Add the paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute. ",
    "Mix in the bulgur, smoked paprika, and smoked salt. ",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and crumbled feta cheese. ",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until the mixture is heated through. ",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired. ",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
  ],
